{"tid":1034670,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【裝滿貨車】強國女出嫁要近千件聘禮 網民：要開超市？","createTime":"2019-02-24T05:54:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-24T08:57:14.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bde4fd56dd562d07e975cfb051801257de0d5be6","tid":1034670,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T05:54:36.000Z","msg":"香港情侶結婚，多寧願「一切從簡」，即使向女方送上的聘禮，可能以禮金代替。惟近日內地網絡熱傳一段的出嫁影片，因影片中貨車上數以百計的聘禮，引發網民熱議。<br />\n事發於上周五（22日），安徽亳州渦陽縣一處農村有女子出閣，女方向男方要求了26種不同的聘禮，每種數量更多達30件。當中還未包括豬肉、煙花等物品，總數近千件聘禮塞滿了貨車。網民紛紛留言，有人形容女方簡直可以開間小型超市，亦有人批評太浮誇，不過有人卻持反對意見，認為一個願打一個願挨就無問題。<br />\n網民意見：<br />\n簡單1988200711：不得不承認，越窮的地方這種事越多......。<br />\n12年義務教育提倡者：浮誇。<br />\n宇宙月亮131：周瑜打黃蓋，一個願打一個願挨。<br />\n搶人時代：別人要車要房，你要超市。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190224/large/1550970696_5e31.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190224%2Flarge%2F1550970696_5e31.jpg&h=902659c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190224/59293924\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190224%2F59293924&d=5l33Zop1uuimQiJtW1o9xapJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=16ab1d79\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190224%2F59293924&h=7ac85db0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190224/59293924</a>"},{"pid":"0a30ecf804c9547a6f7b3109ff8655053c8deb5a","tid":1034670,"uid":56467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T08:32:00.000Z","msg":"直接要錢好過啦"},{"pid":"717d0bc8ae232e9d513d8718a3fa37280de239a8","tid":1034670,"uid":196484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a30ecf804c9547a6f7b3109ff8655053c8deb5a","tid":1034670,"uid":56467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T08:32:00.000Z","msg":"直接要錢好過啦"}